definition: not yet/did not/have not/not/8th earthly branch: 1-3 p.m., 6th solar month (7th July-6th August), year of the Sheep/ancient Chinese compass point: 210°
to count/to count as/to regard as/to enumerate (sb's shortcomings)
erhua variant of 未知數|未知数[wei4 zhi1 shu4]

sentences.english: But he is also the entity K. who is the x of this flesh-and-blood equation.
sentences.chinese: 但是他也是實體的K，是這個肉體等式的未知數x。

sentences.english: Argentina are the unknown package of this World Cup.
sentences.chinese: 阿根廷是這屆世界盃上的一個未知數。

sentences.english: It's still uncertain whether the College Spring Sports will be held this year.
sentences.chinese: 學院今年的春運會是否開還是個未知數。

sentences.english: Not solvable for the unknowns by the same set of values. Used of two or more equations or inequalities.
sentences.chinese: 不可解的同一系列值的情況下由於有未知數而無解的。

sentences.english: It is not known whether SAFS responds to antifungal therapy.
sentences.chinese: 但對抗真菌治療是否有效，仍是未知數。

sentences.english: Now I have two equations with two unknowns.
sentences.chinese: 現在是兩個等式裏有兩個未知數。

sentences.english: The unknown number can be calculated from the data.
sentences.chinese: 通過已知數可以算出未知數。

sentences.english: The extent of other psychopathology in patients with ESRD is largely unknown.
sentences.chinese: 其他ESRD患者的精神問題大部分仍是未知數。

sentences.english: Calculate the unknown in the following.
But it is unclear when dealmaking might return to previous highs.
sentences.chinese: 不過，交易數量能否回到從前的高位還是個未知數。

sentences.english: If you want to get the unknown number, you should know the known number first.
sentences.chinese: 如果要想求出未知數，你首先得知道已知數。

sentences.english: Moreover, it will be wages after the club, which is unknown.
sentences.chinese: 而且，俱樂部之後是否還會欠薪，這也是未知數。

sentences.english: Enrich your life today. Yesterday is history. Tomorrow is mystery.
sentences.chinese: 充實今天的生活，昨曰已成過去，明天還是未知數。

sentences.english: For power users, this might just turn into one of the most important new features on FriendFeed.
sentences.chinese: 即時更新能否讓網站變得更具吸引力還是個未知數。

sentences.english: Palin and Huckabee are the unknowns.
sentences.chinese: 佩林和赫卡比還是未知數。
